author: Unity
description:
In this course created in collaboration with Discord, you'll learn how to integrate the Discord Social SDK’s powerful social features directly into your Unity games, creating engaging experiences that keep players connected both in-game and on Discord.

Check out the course on Unity learn: https://unity3d.info/discord-social-sdk-unity 
Explore the Discord Social SDK: https://unity3d.info/discord-social-sdk
title: Getting started with Discord Social SDK for Unity
